Text:

Yep, Fresh advertise it as 5.56 but have declared 5.57 all over the actual software itself.

Still, can someone seed this! There are 4 peers but no seeds.

Thanks.

Download the "free" trial version here: http://www.freshsw.com/xns/pro/

Now download the blizzard keygen for version 5.5 here on TPB, 

It's called: X-NetStat.Professional.v5.55.Incl.Keygen.BLiZZARD-Deantjah

and register with the Blizzard keygen using any name you want.

That simple.
